'''''CIS Shadowfeed''''', featured in ''[[Star Wars Insider]]'' magazine, was a series of in-universe news articles from a [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatist]] perspective, detailing galactic events during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. The articles are written by [[Pablo Hidalgo]]. CIS Shadowfeed articles were published in ''Star Wars Insider'' issues #65 to #76, after the release of [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']].

